There are four Acquisition Ways that do not appear here but will always show on the animal screens.

They are :

Other Rescue/Shelter/Sanctuary

Owner Surrender

Born at Rescue

Public

Public means that someone from the public brought the animal to you.

Some other common ways that you may want to consider adding are:

Animal Hospital

Stray

Trapped by Shelter

Puppy Mill
